      • createProject

        public ProjectActions createProject(java.lang.String fileExt,
                                    Languages lang)
        Returns an object of type ProjectActions and creates the SettingsWin for the project.

        The first criterion to select a ProjectActions is the file extension. Only if no corresponding class is found the language is used.

        Parameters:
        fileExt - the file extension which a project is to be defined for
        lang - the language which has a value from Languages
        Returns:
        an object of type ProjectActions or null if no class exists that implements ProjectActions for the given file extension.

      • enableActions

        public void enableActions(java.lang.String className,
                          int projCount)
        Enables action components in the menu and toolbar depending on the type of project
        Parameters:
        className - the name of the class of type ProjectActions
        projCount - the number of already configured projects
